    "asOf": "2021-10-27",
    "date": "2022-10-03T18:45:11Z",
    "text": "Emergency Relief for Servicemembers Act of 2021\n\nThis bill authorizes a servicemember to terminate specified contracts (e.g., contracts for commercial mobile service or internet service) that are entered into in relation to military orders for a permanent change of station if the member then receives a stop movement order in response to a local, national, or global emergency which prevents the member from using the services provided under the contract."
